  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个解析器的状态图，描述从初始状态开始处理输入的过程。核心状态有三个：NeedMore表示还需要更多输入，Complete表示解析完成，Error表示出错。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "[*]",
        "NeedMore",
        "Complete",
        "Error"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。所以起点是初始状态，直接进到NeedMore。NeedMore应该是核心状态，可以循环回到自身吗？比如收到more input的时候？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "[*]",
        "NeedMore"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，NeedMore要有自循环，标注为\"more input\"。另外当遇到EOF或者complete信号时，要转到Complete状态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "NeedMore",
        "Complete"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把NeedMore的自循环和到Complete的转移加上。那Error状态是什么情况下进入的？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "NeedMore",
        "Complete"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "当解析过程中遇到错误时，从NeedMore直接跳到Error。标注就写\"error\"就行。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "NeedMore",
        "Error"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加NeedMore到Error的转移。我检查一下：初始状态→NeedMore，NeedMore自循环标注more input，NeedMore→Complete标注EOF/complete，NeedMore→Error标注error。这样对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "[*]",
        "NeedMore",
        "Complete",
        "Error"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，EOF/complete的标注改成\"EOF/complete\"更准确，之前我说得不够清楚。另外确认一下，Complete和Error都是终止状态，不需要再往外转了吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "NeedMore",
        "Complete"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
